# This file defines WHO must approve changes to sacred files.
# GitHub enforces this server-side - NO LOCAL BYPASS POSSIBLE.
#
# Requirements:
# 1. Branch protection must be enabled on main
# 2. "Require review from Code Owners" must be checked
# 3. Direct pushes to main must be blocked
#
# With this config, NO developer can:
# - Create ESLint exceptions
# - Modify build configs
# - Disable VRP checks
# - Change security scripts
# - Bypass Husky hooks
# - Modify custom rules
#
# WITHOUT Ken's explicit approval.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

